<section name="297">
	<p>
		The market is held in a warren of booths set up in a roofed arcade at the eastern edge of town. Items with no purchase price are not available locally.
	</p>
	<market>
		<header type="armour"/>
		<armour name="leather" bonus="1" buy="60" sell="45"/>
		<armour name="ring mail" bonus="2" buy="120" sell="90"/>
		<armour name="chain mail" bonus="3" buy="240" sell="180"/>

		<header type="weapon"/>
		<weapon bonus="0" buy="50" sell="40"/>
		<weapon bonus="1" buy="250" sell="200"/>
		<weapon bonus="2" sell="400"/>

		<header type="magic"/>
		<tool name="amber wand" ability="magic" bonus="1" sell="300"/>

		<header type="other"/>
		<tool name="compass" ability="scouting" bonus="1" buy="500" sell="400"/>
		<tool name="cross-staff" ability="scouting" bonus="2" buy="900" sell="700"/>
		<tool name="sextant" ability="scouting" bonus="3" buy="1300" sell="1100"/>
		<item name="lantern" buy="80" sell="40"/>
		<item name="selenium ore" sell="700"/>
	</market>
	<p>
		If you have a ship and want to load a cargo of copper ore, you should visit the mines. When you&#8217;re through here, <goto section="99"/>.
	</p>
</section>
